description.en: Since the launching of the CoinBene Perpetual Contract, it has been fallen in love by customers. In order to promote it much better, CoinBene will issue the perpetual contract token CFT（CoinBene Future Token） soon. CFT（CoinBene Future Token）token is the only rights and interests representation of CoinBene Perpetual Contract. Total issuance volume is 1 billion CFT（CoinBene Future Token）.
